Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亞城木君短篇新作的NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒~我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.57,0:00:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是關於什麼的漫畫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是出現了黑惡魔和白惡魔就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之很有趣 請先讀一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但總不會比新妻老師的殭屍更有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個主人公的戰鬥場面畫得好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和以往亞城木的作品不同的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次不再是邪道漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是以王道戰鬥漫畫的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與此相對的 這次新妻君的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以殭屍為主人公並與人類戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以說是引入了邪道的王道戰鬥漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.92,0:00:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把邪道提升到王道的亞城木夢葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:01:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在王道中引入邪道的新妻英二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.23,0:01:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說是新妻老師和亞城木老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相帶著對方的意識創作出來的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們之間相互產生了積極的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底誰會贏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是新妻君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是輸贏的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使兩篇都可以刊登
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會在同一期上刊登吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果連續刊登的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短篇要準備三篇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還只有兩篇而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快給我多拿些稿子來啊 快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！副編輯長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:13.17,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,480)\c&HFFFFFF&}週刊和月刊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」已經決定在4月17日發售的20期上刊登了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\an8}太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉我們提出這麼強人所難的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為無論如何都想讓佐佐木編輯長調走前能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 雖然突然讓我看NAME的時候我有點吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒理由不提交那麼有趣的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是只有現在的亞城木夢葉才能畫出來的王道戰鬥漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能讓真城君接一下電話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在前一期上會刊登新妻君的短篇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎樣都會被比較一番的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為王道漫畫來比較
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畫風的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒目的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精彩場面的連頁以及分格的張弛度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 看來你已經比我還清楚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油畫出出色的原稿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新妻君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」已經決定在19期刊登了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解！我終於邁出了走向世界的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後的一期上會刊登亞城木君的短篇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢~好想快點看到哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次亞城木君也挑戰王道戰鬥漫畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不辛辣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是相當辛辣的王道戰鬥漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nice亞城木夢葉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nice辛辣的王道戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別太用功哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按現在的進度時間很充足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我明白 但我想畫出比英二更好的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞豆發來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說已經確定擔任女主角了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:05:00.43,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H3C3E3E&\3c&HEFF2EF&\frz-16\an8\move(852,340,850,265}新角色確定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:05:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經確定擔任Young Kick「即興12」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女主角經理人小眼的聲優了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是人氣相當高的足球漫畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我們被打敗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被亞豆超過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要讓她的第一個JACK作品女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來自我們的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要讓「REVERSI」動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給亞豆準備好女主角的位置！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz10.5\c&H7B7C78&\3c&HF5FBF7&\shad0\fs33\b0\pos(780,114)}Re：新角色確定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz10.5\c&H7B7C78&\3c&HF5FBF7&\shad0\fs33\b0\pos(710,276)}恭喜你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz12\c&H7B7C78&\3c&HF5FBF7&\shad0\fs33\b0\pos(822,288)}又給了我很多幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz13.5\c&H7B7C78&\3c&HF5FBF7&\shad0\fs33\b0\pos(746,476)}我定會追趕上你來實現夢想！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞豆小姐將來要擔當女主角的我們的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要讓它成為聲優亞豆美保的第一代表作！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是19期的樣刊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」上了封面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓短篇作品上封面 這還是頭一遭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是新編輯長的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也說明對新妻君有十分大的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 特殊待遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不甘心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能超過他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超過連續20周保持第一完結「CROW」的新妻英二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」第1位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然已經有所預料 但是居然能拿這麼多票
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新妻英二果然是牛人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是奔著世界第一去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真的嗎 雄二郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說叫我班長啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好好 班長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,692票
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說這是短篇的最高紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英二果然不是蓋的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然這樣才是新妻英二啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我們的勝負還未見分曉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 請你盡快畫「ZOMBIE☆GUN」的連載NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到開會之前 請盡全力畫的盡可能出彩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 這麼老實 你一點兒都不高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高興並燃燒著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20號的本報
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」第1位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「PCP」第4
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說還刷新了短篇紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是上周的「ZOMBIE☆GUN」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 是超過了「ZOMBIE☆GUN」的692票
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這周的「REVERSI」以694票刷新紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇！給力！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給力啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才說我有自信嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂說 你什麼時候說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣嗎 但我當時就覺得應該能行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要給香耶打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我給亞豆發短信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒想到一個禮拜就被刷新了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上頭已經說用「ZOMBIE☆GUN」開始連載
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周就到NAME的截稿期限了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因為這點小事就失去幹勁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」也要進行連載嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…亞城木君還有「PCP」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:09:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要同時連載兩部 從現狀來看有困難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然要連載「ZOMBIE☆GUN」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也想讓「REVERSI」連載吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經做好心理準備你們會這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會跟上面傳達的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連載用的第1話的NAME我們已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話請過目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有意思 比起短篇還要好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 比起「PCP」還能更上一個台階
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咋回事嘛 雄二郎… 不…班長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新妻他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輸了兩票 還說什麼征服世界太可笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我還不能出連載NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也太浪費了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班長 這是「REVERSI」的連載NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 你放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新妻君和亞城木君每人兩部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合計四部這種事明擺著不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 會連載「ZOMBIE☆GUN」和「REVERSI」中有趣的那部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會發生那種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮JACK的現狀 肯定是優先新妻君的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優先自己負責的作家 這未免有點過分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 亞城木君每週能畫兩部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰說不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哪來的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他們是二人組
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們自己也說要畫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊兩個 適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NAME無可挑剔很有意思 沒有理由不讓登吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們正在連載「PCP」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就讓「PCP」完結
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能別說得這麼輕巧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「PCP」可是打算出中學生編的人氣漫畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就同時連載兩部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…的確有困難
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為連載「TRAP」的時候曾因過度疲勞住過院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓他們勉強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事想找您商量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於「REVERSI」的短篇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是以怎樣的意向讓他們刊登的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼處理「REVERSI」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓶子 這已經是你該決定的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 請容許我作為「週刊少年JACK」的編輯長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與「必勝JACK」編輯長商量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那之後就渺無音訊 是不是意味著無法上連載會議啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是服部先生打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「可不可以登在必勝JACK上」 我不太明白您的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」要在「必勝JACK」上連載嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:12:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 每月一回的話應該能和週刊的「PCP」兩部同時連載主編是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」連載
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把「ZOMBIE☆GUN」的分鏡提交到連載會議上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我已經完全明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我很狂傲的說了要創作出世界第一的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的對手不是世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是亞城木老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」的對手是「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 不是「PCP」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是「REVERSI」是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和登刊的雜誌沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為明顯是「REVERSI」更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然打算竭盡全力讓兩部作品都在週刊上連載
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在月刊「必勝JACK」上連載
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話真是鬆了口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我們來說這是最好的結果了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的結果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我盡快介紹你們認識「REVERSI」的擔當編輯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然在「必勝」上連載的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也必須要他們的人來做擔當編輯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然知道你們同時連載兩部作品會很吃緊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 也還請你們不要讓「PCP」下滑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會比之前更加努力的去畫「PCP」的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服部先生好像有點寂寞吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 說實話我們也是想讓服部來負責的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這麼說的話 也只是我們的任性罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是沒有辦法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能對作者和作品過分投入的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:14:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我真的很想做「REVERSI」的擔當編輯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定能成為出色的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算在「週刊少年JACK」上也能成為頂樑柱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直伴隨亞城木他們成長的我最清楚不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新妻君也說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起「PCP」明顯是「REVERSI」更加有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 他們畫出了這麼讓人期望的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 說到底我們也只是個上班族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能遵從上司的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了 這些我都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我還是想說我很想做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 真的很想做「REVERSI」的編輯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 本來的話 應該是我到你們那去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們特地跑過來真是對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還慌慌忙忙的整理了資料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中野現在是「必勝JACK」的副編輯長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:15:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓副編輯長來做我們的編輯 真是信心大增啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這邊的陣容還比較薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很期待「REVERSI」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才是 很高興都夠連載
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣以來就只有一部能開新連載啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的只有新妻君的「ZOMBIE☆GUN」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就一部的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不這回的一部先放著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下次湊滿三部再一起開怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」應該盡早連載吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓「REVERSI」連載不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 你還在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為擔心亞城木君在週刊上同時連載兩部會很吃緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才放到「必勝」上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓「PCP」在「必勝」上連載
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而「REVERSI」在JACK上連載
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 扭轉已經決定的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 說不定有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩部新連載的話還說得過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 太形式主義了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在讀者層廣泛的「必勝」上內容有更大發揮空間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對「PCP」來說也是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」從票數來看可是比「ZOMBIE☆GUN」還要高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起「PCP」新妻君也更加在意「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能在「週刊少年JACK」上和「ZOMBIE☆GUN」一決高下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服部也是比起「PCP」更想擔當「REVERSI」的編輯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服部他是這麼說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不說我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我是班長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是連載會議中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了 到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是現在我正和亞城木君在討論啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓亞城木君也去連載會議？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 為什麼連我們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去一趟比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就直問了  服部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對「REVERSI」在「必勝JACK」上連載有何看法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…能實現「REVERSI」連載我認為是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞城木君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬分的感謝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是問你們這些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是問「PCP」和「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們想讓哪部在「週刊少年JACK」上連載
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是把你們的真心話說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想在週刊上連載哪部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R…「REVERSI」已經定下在「必勝」上連載…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就算問想在哪裡連載
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服部 說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓「REVERSI」在「週刊少年JACK」上連載
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲 連你都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想在週刊上畫「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將「PCP」放到「必勝JACK」連載
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」決定在「週刊少年JACK」上連載
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 都這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 比起這個 能聽到服部先生的心聲我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真城君 高木君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們必須將「REVERSI」變為「週刊少年JACK」的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這一定是能成為支柱的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我自說自話了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你做了一個很好的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」的潛力只有週刊才能發揮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「PCP」在自由度較高的我們這裡發表才更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班長們也說了同樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是雄二郎 他做班長的工作超過了我們的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道謝還太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是「REVERSI」10周就完結了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們兩個可就都沒立場了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓它成為頂尖的漫畫的 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 頂尖的會是「ZOMBIE☆GUN」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待今後的「週刊少年JACK」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓶子 你變得很有JACK編輯長的樣子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「REVERSI」的連載轉到「週刊少年JACK」上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 有幹勁了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小河先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像說要完結一部現在連載的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以又可以來幫我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小河先生啊 他很可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 既然連載了2部 就得比之前更抓緊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是再加一個人的話這個工作室是不是有點擠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 移一移沙發的話應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我不想離開這個工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以我打算從爺爺那買下這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 那我也出一半的錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用啦 是叔叔的工作室嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想買下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最高 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在和那個女孩子交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,額 算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼突然問這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 給你了 拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筆記本？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是信弘的日記
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒也稱不上是日記 不過敘述了對某個女性的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我怎麼能收這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的啦 沒什麼大不了的 你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔和亞豆的媽媽中學也是同桌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an8\shad0\fs35\bord0\frz25\frx-2\move(612,188,524,65)\fad(500,0)}我想和春野美雪結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an8\shad0\bord0\fs35\frz25\fad(500,0)\move(682,336,594,213)}在那之前我會在筆記裡記錄下對她的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an8\shad0\bord0\frz25\fs35\frx-2\fad(500,0)\move(906,594,818,471)}然後 我認為變成老爺爺和老婆婆的時候\N如果還能一起笑著看這本\N筆記是最幸福的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來叔叔在想這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某種意義上來說這能妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 這不是妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔是認真在落實著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 收到了亞豆媽媽要和別人結婚的信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an8\shad0\bord0\frz17\fs30\fad(500,0)\pos(722,116)}今年生日當天也收到了春野的信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an8\shad0\bord0\frz17\fs30\fad(500,0)\pos(758,146)}她也想著我呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an5\shad0\frz17\fs40\fad(500,0)\pos(744,368)\3c&HE1EAE9&}一定要盡快成為一流的漫畫家！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an8\shad0\bord0\frz17\fs30\fad(500,0)\pos(348,604)}計劃都已經做好了\N只剩下決定求婚的話了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H63736B&\an8\shad0\bord0\frz17\fs30\fad(500,0)\pos(1072,518)}趁此給春野10封寫好的信讓她選擇吧？…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.63,0:22:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是最後的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔沒能做成的事 想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.80,0:22:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來完成
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為JACK的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.03,0:24:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於要開始連載兩部了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.80,0:24:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要把兩部都畫得很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.37,0:24:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是「REVERSI」可能堅持不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.05,0:24:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 延時和一鼓作氣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.43,0:24:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要選哪個夢想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
